1. Every client needs to create a converter to convert the date string from ical
   angular, java, ios, ... 
   mainframe: cobol
     
2. It's quite important for maintainability of your software to always store times in UTC. 
    If you ever store in your local timezone, calculating any other timezone will be a mess 
    - think daylight savings times, change of timezones of different areas of the world etc.
    
    not reliable
    
    

